{"tid":1877102,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情股 831 有無得諗？","createTime":"2020-02-12T22:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T06:31:27.000Z","uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ffb78a9bb449ebba5dc5bf0abcde64c662f339","tid":1877102,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T22:14:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2020-02-13<br />\n最強疫情股香港電視（1137）配股後再有新消息，旗下HKTVmall公司宣佈為處理積壓的定單，2月調整短期免運費金額，最低門檻調升至800元，幅度高達六成。此招一出，相信會令部份客戶卻步，但措施只是暫時性，中長線客戶必定會回流，待股價調整過後，重拾升軌並非難事。<br />\n<br />\n為應付爆升客量，集團稱已與多個知名零售連鎖店商討，拓展訂單自取網絡，森信紙業（731）旗下Foodwise乃其中一員，股價單日曾爆升三成，759阿信屋母公司CEC國際（759）、<del>優品360</del>（2360）亦炒個不亦樂乎。不過，從分店數目、物流經驗及營運理念看，利亞零售（831）旗下OK便利店才是最佳拍檔。<br />\n<br />\n講分店，全港OK便利店數目達339間，為759阿信屋的1.9倍。講經驗，除與內地物流龍頭順豐合作外，最新亦與百貨送遞服務「pandamart」合作，要應付HKTVmall大量定單，易如反掌。講良心，港視買口罩機為港人服務，OK便利店亦向長者派發免費口罩。公司坐擁逾5億元淨現金，配合穩定的利潤表現及逾六厘股息，炒到飛天無難度。<br />\n<br />\n唐牛<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/tongcow88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Ftongcow88&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=a5b01ca1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/tongcow88</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c61a864da5ba7d5dd8818a431c3947e3a34a5f","tid":1877102,"uid":89538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:23:08.000Z","msg":"我有批口罩好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c7816694c2ac1aeacee9ed1ae762b9c9d94e6e","tid":1877102,"uid":199559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:25:47.000Z","msg":"唔可能啦 ok店邊有位<br />\n平時已經迫到七彩<br />\n寫文嗰個用下個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055106dac8a235555fa6a31516092c845a78cd44","tid":1877102,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T01:45:41.000Z","msg":"一向無成交"},{"pid":"3da1a3b11ae1bd8a9c1a4df018c8904ed7bb08c4","tid":1877102,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"今日先專登買夠1000 等佢送貨<br />\nVip day減完都要900幾"}]}